szakacs.kpi.fei.tuke.misc

Class GDXRectangle

  • java.lang.Object
    • szakacs.kpi.fei.tuke.misc.GDXRectangle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Rectangle
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GDXActorRectangle

    public class GDXRectangle
extends java.lang.Object
implements Rectangle

    The libGDX specific implementation of the Rectangle interface for a game object descriptor.

    The current implementation uses libGDX with its coordinate origin at lower left. The lower left corner set of coordinates is returned by Rectangle.getRectangleX() and Rectangle.getRectangleY()).
